It seems like there are a lot of people vying for that Okinawa trip with you

517
00:33:27,730 --> 00:33:32,610
so I figured that I need to come up with a good proposal,

518
00:33:36,170 --> 00:33:37,850
yet...

519
00:33:39,300 --> 00:33:42,680
you look irresistible in a yukata

520
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:46,040
and now that I think about it, this is a hot-spring date!

521
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:48,480
That's why

522
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:50,100
I...

523
00:33:51,080 --> 00:33:52,940
got all panicked.

524
00:33:58,040 --> 00:33:59,860
So

525
00:34:00,990 --> 00:34:03,650
I'm really sorry

526
00:34:03,650 --> 00:34:05,180
if I ended up

527
00:34:06,120 --> 00:34:07,860
hurting you because of that.

528
00:34:15,190 --> 00:34:16,690
Um,

529
00:34:18,620 --> 00:34:20,780
if you'll allow me to say one thing...

530
00:34:22,020 --> 00:34:26,390
I've been truly happy lately.

531
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:32,840
Sometimes I panic and spin my wheels,

532
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:35,770
but just being with you

533
00:34:35,770 --> 00:34:39,990
makes my heart feel full.

534
00:34:45,620 --> 00:34:47,260
But, you know what?

535
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:54,030
If

536
00:34:56,500 --> 00:34:58,790
you seriously

537
00:35:01,620 --> 00:35:04,460
want to get closer to me

538
00:35:06,030 --> 00:35:07,420
or

539
00:35:08,180 --> 00:35:10,630
feel like you're missing

540
00:35:12,050 --> 00:35:14,240
something today

541
00:35:16,520 --> 00:35:20,610
then I feel the same way.

542
00:35:23,090 --> 00:35:25,040
Yamamoto.

543
00:35:26,910 --> 00:35:28,520
So

544
00:35:32,440 --> 00:35:34,750
if you feel the same way

545
00:35:45,470 --> 00:35:46,940
let's

546
00:35:48,320 --> 00:35:50,780
go back to our room.

547
00:36:20,340 --> 00:36:22,250
Please tell me

548
00:36:23,930 --> 00:36:25,970
if there's anything you

549
00:36:28,910 --> 00:36:30,520
like or dislike.

550
00:36:31,570 --> 00:36:33,670
Tell me everything, please.

551
00:36:43,700 --> 00:36:45,100
I

552
00:36:50,810 --> 00:36:52,680
want to know everything.

553
00:36:56,440 --> 00:36:57,800
Okay.

554
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:05,000
Also,

555
00:37:09,660 --> 00:37:12,290
I really want to cherish today

556
00:37:14,680 --> 00:37:17,200
but I'm sorry if I can't perform.

557
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:24,180
Yamamoto.

558
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:26,650
Maybe...

559
00:37:27,620 --> 00:37:29,050
Yes?

560
00:37:30,290 --> 00:37:32,200
Maybe...

561
00:37:33,560 --> 00:37:35,820
I should be the one saying that.

562
00:37:38,820 --> 00:37:41,960
I mean, I'm the older one here

563
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:47,300
and I'm the one who should be in the position to care for you.

564
00:37:47,300 --> 00:37:49,310
Care?

565
00:37:49,310 --> 00:37:51,370
No.

566
00:37:51,370 --> 00:37:54,790
That's got nothing to do with age. It's my job.

567
00:37:54,790 --> 00:37:57,570
No, but I...

568
00:37:57,570 --> 00:38:00,730
was and still am your husband before I became your girlfriend.

569
00:38:00,730 --> 00:38:03,730
Well, if you're going to bring that up,

570
00:38:03,730 --> 00:38:07,330
then I'm both your wife and boyfriend.

571
00:38:08,350 --> 00:38:10,440
Honestly, what are we rambling about?!

572
00:38:10,440 --> 00:38:12,280
You're right.

573
00:38:23,340 --> 00:38:25,590
Listen, Yamamoto.

574
00:38:26,610 --> 00:38:27,950
Yes?

575
00:38:30,780 --> 00:38:32,620
Let's do this, together.

576
00:38:35,650 --> 00:38:39,190
Dreams...

577
00:38:39,190 --> 00:38:41,680
Husband, girlfriend, boyfriend,

578
00:38:42,350 --> 00:38:45,320
older or younger...

579
00:38:46,190 --> 00:38:50,520
I don't think any of that matters right now.

580
00:38:52,200 --> 00:38:55,530
I also want to know

581
00:38:55,530 --> 00:38:57,650
what you like

582
00:38:58,670 --> 00:39:01,350
and what you dislike.

583
00:39:12,050 --> 00:39:13,600
So...

584
00:39:15,060 --> 00:39:16,990
Let's do this,

585
00:39:17,770 --> 00:39:19,350
together.

586
00:39:21,120 --> 00:39:22,440
Okay.

587
00:39:57,360 --> 00:39:59,470
[I will not lay a finger on Hayami today!]

588
00:39:59,470 --> 00:40:04,200
When did you get this temporary tattoo made?

589
00:40:04,200 --> 00:40:06,210
It's done!

590
00:40:06,210 --> 00:40:08,350
The proposal I've put my heart and soul into creating!

591
00:40:08,350 --> 00:40:09,910
[All Housework Tasks Sharing App]

592
00:40:09,910 --> 00:40:12,270
I have to text Hayami right away!

593
00:40:12,270 --> 00:40:15,800
You should save it for later. Look at how late it is.

594
00:40:15,800 --> 00:40:19,190
12:07 a.m.?! That means...

595
00:40:19,190 --> 00:40:22,930
"Today" is over...

596
00:40:22,930 --> 00:40:27,040
Come on, that's splitting hairs!

597
00:40:27,040 --> 00:40:29,540
In any case, you can't bother them.

598
00:40:29,540 --> 00:40:33,490
You don't want to end their relationship, Koga?!

599
00:40:34,280 --> 00:40:36,470
Well, I suppose I might be the one

600
00:40:36,470 --> 00:40:41,450
who ends up stopping them.

601
00:40:44,580 --> 00:40:48,300
Gosh, I'm starting to get nervous.

602
00:40:48,300 --> 00:40:49,910
You'll be fine.

603
00:40:49,910 --> 00:40:53,970
I think the fridge with back-up power is a great idea.

604
00:40:55,280 --> 00:40:57,900
I actually shelved that idea.

605
00:40:57,900 --> 00:40:58,930
What?

606
00:40:58,930 --> 00:41:03,490
Thanks to you, I've come up with an idea

607
00:41:03,490 --> 00:41:05,050
that's more like us.

608
00:41:05,050 --> 00:41:06,660
Really?

609
00:41:08,580 --> 00:41:12,060
Here. Take a look at this, if you like.

610
00:41:12,060 --> 00:41:13,610
Okay.

611
00:41:13,610 --> 00:41:15,750
Okay, I'm off.

612
00:41:17,970 --> 00:41:22,920
Handheld All-in-One Vacuum Cleaner.
[Proposal for a new style of cleaning]

613
00:41:24,980 --> 00:41:28,800
What I am proposing is a stick-type

614
00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:31,980
and handheld vacuum cleaner set.

615
00:41:31,980 --> 00:41:34,920
Existing products are made

616
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:39,650
with the assumption that only one person will use them.

617
00:41:39,650 --> 00:41:41,310
As such,

618
00:41:41,310 --> 00:41:45,620
cleaning ends up being the job of one person.

619
00:41:46,820 --> 00:41:50,640
However, with this product

620
00:41:50,640 --> 00:41:54,820
two people can use the regular vacuum and the handheld vacuum cleaner at the same time.

621
00:41:54,820 --> 00:41:58,400
Cleaning should not be done on your own.

622
00:41:58,400 --> 00:42:00,060
I believe it can become a household chore

623
00:42:00,880 --> 00:42:04,810
that can be done with someone else.

624
00:42:08,800 --> 00:42:11,960
What? No winning proposals?!

625
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:14,310
So no winning trip to Okinawa?

626
00:42:14,310 --> 00:42:16,890
Well, that's how it seems.

627
00:42:16,890 --> 00:42:18,200
No way...

628
00:42:18,200 --> 00:42:22,050
Now, now, don't be like that. I have to apologize to you too, Yamamoto.

629
00:42:22,050 --> 00:42:23,780
No, that's okay.

630
00:42:23,780 --> 00:42:27,100
This whole contest has given me a little boost in confidence.

631
00:42:27,100 --> 00:42:30,380
I will view this as a starting point and do my best.

632
00:42:39,970 --> 00:42:41,650
Koga?

633
00:42:43,090 --> 00:42:44,630
Hayami.

634
00:42:44,630 --> 00:42:45,840
Heading out to get some sales?

635
00:42:45,840 --> 00:42:47,780
Yes, just the one.

636
00:42:47,780 --> 00:42:51,240
It's a shame about the contest.

637
00:42:51,240 --> 00:42:54,120
Well, I had a feeling it would end up like this.

638
00:42:54,120 --> 00:42:58,160
Despite what they say, big corporations have lots of hurdles and hoops.

639
00:42:58,160 --> 00:43:00,270
They really do.

640
00:43:00,270 --> 00:43:04,100
I hope the company becomes more open.

641
00:43:05,640 --> 00:43:08,380
Or perhaps we need to get outside

642
00:43:08,380 --> 00:43:10,780
if we want openness.

643
00:43:10,780 --> 00:43:12,170
What?

644
00:43:14,140 --> 00:43:15,700
Hayami.

645
00:43:19,620 --> 00:43:21,370
Oh, it's Yamamoto.

646
00:43:21,370 --> 00:43:22,550
Hey, what's up?

647
00:43:22,550 --> 00:43:26,430
Hayami, can I buy some expensive meat tonight

648
00:43:26,430 --> 00:43:29,220
to celebrate the end to the contest?

649
00:43:29,900 --> 00:43:34,000
Of course. I'll try to get home as early as possible.

650
00:43:34,000 --> 00:43:35,800
Bye.

651
00:43:35,800 --> 00:43:37,680
Anyway, I should get going.

652
00:43:55,040 --> 00:43:56,470
Hello?

653
00:43:58,400 --> 00:44:01,970
Yes, it's okay.

654
00:44:03,530 --> 00:44:07,900
I've already decided on who I want to take there.

655
00:44:09,900 --> 00:44:11,390
[NEXT EPISODE]

