00:44:11,390 --> 00:44:13,120
Chihiro.

657
00:44:14,080 --> 00:44:16,110
I think...

658
00:44:16,110 --> 00:44:20,570
it's better for us to keep a distance now.

659
00:44:20,570 --> 00:44:22,910
Does that mean you want a breakup?
